# Unit Test Runner

When running unit tests:

1. Read [.ai/skills/unit-test-runner/SKILL.md](.ai/skills/unit-test-runner/SKILL.md)
2. Capture raw output to `docs/exec-plans/raw-test-output/{plan-id}-unit-raw.txt`
3. Run `./.ai/scripts/analyze-maven-test-output.sh <raw-file>` to determine success/failure
4. Consider both exit code and analysis result when reporting pass/fail
